Text: Very poorly tagged. Took me ages to sort out.

I appreciate the upload but you should really tag your audio files before sharing them with the world. Again, I'm not complaing since this is free, but in order to help you and your downloaders get the most out these torrents, I would suggest you tag them with the proper information, including album artwork.
